The paper deals with the discrete Fr\'echet distance, which is a popular measure for comparing polygonal curves, and proposes an algorithm for the discrete Fr\'echet distance under translation. This involves constructing an arrangement of disks and updating reachability in a directed grid graph. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the Computational Geometry (cs.CG), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM), Computational Complexity (cs.CC), and Graph Theory (cs.GT) sub-categories of arXiv CS.
